snippet.title: ANGST: A TALE OF SURVIVAL [Cinematic Trailer]
snippet.description:
Wishlist "ANGST: A TALE OF SURVIVAL" on Steam! https://store.steampowered.com/app/2949910/ANGST_A_TALE_OF_SURVIVAL/

ANGST is a wilderness survival game set in a freezing limbo-like land. Brave the hostile Hollow, craft tools and weapons, hunt, fish, and fight to stay alive. Upgrade skills to venture deeper into the wild, but be warned: what lurks there can thwart your plans. Survive the ANGST!
